我不知道
I don't know.

279
00:17:33,440 --> 00:17:34,480
我只是肯定
But what I do know is that

280
00:17:34,490 --> 00:17:37,620
菲波纳奇 会在下月作证
If Fibonacci testifies next month

281
00:17:37,630 --> 00:17:39,970
我快要成为你的邻居了
You and I are gonna be neighbours.

282
00:17:39,980 --> 00:17:42,520
我不会让这一切发生
And I am not going to let that happen

283
