298
00:18:50,850 --> 00:18:51,730
爹地
Daddy!

299
00:18:51,740 --> 00:18:54,890
你听到那消息了吗
Did you hear the news?

300
00:18:54,900 --> 00:18:57,640
什么消息
What... what news?

301
00:18:57,650 --> 00:18:59,360
我们会和 菲利 叔叔
We're going to stay with Uncle Philly

302
00:18:59,370 --> 00:19:00,780
一起到湖边玩几个星期
At the lake for a few weeks

303
00:19:00,790 --> 00:19:04,480
是的 我们会玩得很开心
Yeah, and we're gonna have a good time.

304
00:19:04,490 --> 00:19:07,230
你是对的 约翰
You're right, John

305
00:19:07,240 --> 00:19:09,320
我确实信任你
Maybe you're right.I do trust you.

306
