312
00:19:38,310 --> 00:19:39,940
我们订婚了
We're engaged

313
00:19:39,950 --> 00:19:41,300
而且
Besides

314
00:19:41,310 --> 00:19:45,000
我一向安分守纪
I got that coming to me because I ain't caused no static in this place

