就因为你的肥皂
Because of your little bar of soap.

354
00:22:10,640 --> 00:22:13,260
我必须先测试一下你会不会泄密
I had to see if you could keep a secret.

355
00:22:13,270 --> 00:22:14,500
你要秘密
You want a secret?

356
00:22:14,510 --> 00:22:16,310
我告诉你个秘密
I got a secret for you, fish

357
00:22:16,320 --> 00:22:18,140
你在我的牢房乱搞
You dig in my cell when I'm there

358
00:22:18,150 --> 00:22:20,640
