Nice out here.

644
00:40:15,500 --> 00:40:16,170
我有一个朋友
I've got a buddy.

645
00:40:16,200 --> 00:40:18,730
在这附近的森林有栋房子
He's got a place way back up in these woods.

646
00:40:18,760 --> 00:40:21,500
